---
import PageLayout from '../../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Cookie policy | Académie Évolution"
  description="How we use cookies and similar technologies."
  lang="en"
>
  <section class="relative z-20 border-0">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
      <span class="tag anim-fade-up" style="--delay:.2s">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mt-4 anim-slide-l" style="--delay:.35s">Cookie policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/60 mt-3 anim-fade-up" style="--delay:.5s">Last updated: March 17, 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-8 text-sm text-white/65 leading-relaxed">
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.1s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">What is a cookie?</h2>
          <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device. They help the site remember preferences and understand usage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.15s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Essential cookies</h2>
          <p>Required for basic site operation (navigation, secure access, forms). They can’t be disabled without affecting functionality.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.2s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Analytics</h2>
          <p>We may use analytics cookies to understand usage and improve the experience. Data is aggregated where possible. You can disable them in your browser.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.25s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Managing cookies</h2>
          <p>Most browsers let you control cookies in settings. Blocking cookies may affect how the site works.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.3s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p><a href="mailto:info@academieevolution.com" class="underline hover:text-white transition">info@academieevolution.com</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
